msgid "{avatar} heard a hidden clue in the market rumors of {location}: {fragment}"
msgstr "{avatar} heard a hidden clue in the market rumors of {location}: {fragment}"

msgid "{avatar} glimpsed a corner of the truth through a mysterious insight: {fragment}"
msgstr "{avatar} glimpsed a corner of the truth through a mysterious insight: {fragment}"

msgid "{avatar} noticed an unusual clue at {location}: {fragment}"
msgstr "{avatar} noticed an unusual clue at {location}: {fragment}"

msgid "{avatar} connected scattered clues and finally learned a world secret capable of shaking this realm's foundations."
msgstr "{avatar} connected scattered clues and finally learned a world secret capable of shaking this realm's foundations."

msgid "{avatar} has pieced together scattered clues and learned a world secret capable of shaking this realm's foundations. If revealed, the secret will become known to all under heaven; if kept silent, only {avatar} will bear it. Complete secret: {secret}"
msgstr "{avatar} has pieced together scattered clues and learned a world secret capable of shaking this realm's foundations. If revealed, the secret will become known to all under heaven; if kept silent, only {avatar} will bear it. Complete secret: {secret}"

msgid "Reveal the world secret?"
msgstr "Reveal the world secret?"

msgid "You have learned a secret capable of shaking the world's foundations. Will you tell all under heaven, or remain silent alone?"
msgstr "You have learned a secret capable of shaking the world's foundations. Will you tell all under heaven, or remain silent alone?"

msgid "Tell everyone"
msgstr "Tell everyone"

msgid "Reveal the complete secret so all cultivators under heaven know this realm's truth."
msgstr "Reveal the complete secret so all cultivators under heaven know this realm's truth."

msgid "Bear it silently"
msgstr "Bear it silently"

msgid "Do not spread it; bear this truth alone."
msgstr "Do not spread it; bear this truth alone."

msgid "{avatar} revealed a world secret to all: '{title}'. From now on, cultivators under heaven know this realm's truth."
msgstr "{avatar} revealed a world secret to all: '{title}'. From now on, cultivators under heaven know this realm's truth."

msgid "{avatar} chose silence after learning the truth, pressing this secret deep into the heart."
msgstr "{avatar} chose silence after learning the truth, pressing this secret deep into the heart."
